# @desc   Switch the bottom navigation tab from Home to Spend (legacy name: Reports). Triggers the ManualNavigateToReports Sentry span end-to-end (BottomTab click -> Spend screen layout completion). Assumes the user is signed in and the bottom nav bar is visible.
# @pre    text="Home"
# @pre    text="Spend"
# @post   text="Spend"
# @tag    navigation
# @tag    perf
# @tag    sentry-ManualNavigateToReports
press "label=\"Home\""
press "label=\"Spend\""
